Two generals and two colonels in the
Syrian military were among 160 Syrians who crossed the border
into  Turkey  seeking refuge, the state-run Anatolia news agency
reported.  About 44,000 Syrians have fled to Turkey to escape the
violence in their country, and the number of military defections
has been increasing, Anatolia said, citing the prime ministerâ€™s
